beer.beer_description:
What exactly is a cold IPA anyway?
Is it an IPA? Kinda.
Is it a lager? Yes, technically.

All we know is, we’ve combined the clean, crisp malt base typical of a lager, amped it up a bit, added a West Coast IPA dry hope regime (Idaho 7 & Citra), and fermented it with lager yeast, at lager temperatures.

Confusing? Perhaps.
Refreshing and delicious? Definitely.
